markets.title: How low will Bitcoin get this year?
markets.subtitle: $70,000.01 or above
markets.rules_primary: If the price of Bitcoin is below 70000 by Dec 31, 2025 at 11:59 PM ET, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: The Contract is settled by taking an average of CF Benchmarks' Bitcoin Real-Time Index (BRTI) in any sixty second period, excluding the top 20% and bottom 20% of values. Data is used 24/7 to resolve the contract.
markets.early_close_condition: If this event occurs, the market will close the following 10am ET.
